title: Israeli parliament votes to dissolve, triggering fifth election in four years
content:
1. Israeli parliament votes to dissolve, triggering fifth election in four years  CNN
  2. MKs to try again Thursday to disperse Knesset, set elections, as wrangling goes on  The Times of Israel
  3. Israel Sets New Election, Spotlighting Role of Arab Minority in Government  The Wall Street Journal
  4. Israeli parliament dissolves, Lapid to become acting prime minister  Axios
